@tool_tip.string: The name is limited to 63 characters. Longer prim names are cut short. Names can only consist of printable characters found in the ASCII-7 (non-extended) character set, with the exception of the vertical bar/pipe '|'.

When people have 'Hover Tips on All Objects' selected in the viewer's settings, they'll see the object description pop-up for any object under their mouse pointer. The prim description is limited to 127 bytes any string longer then that will be truncated.
